data.title: Royal Jewels of the World Message Board: Re: Diamond bow brooch HRH Princess Léa of Belgium
data.text:
Unfortunately, I don't know anything about the origins of this bracelet.

During the wedding dinner for Crown Prince Leka II and Crown Princess Elia of Albania, Princess Lea also wore an nice diamond bow brooch on her corsage, as well as diamond earrings. I do not remember to have seen it ealier on her, or on Princess Lilian, or on any other Belgian royal lady.
